0 upper normal limit or bilirubin > 7.5 mg/dL, do not use</li></ul><b>Renal(Kidney)</b><ul><li>Cisplatin:<br>If CrCl 30-60 mL/min, reduce dose by 50%   <br>                                                                   If CrCl < 30 mL/min, do not use</li><li>Paclitaxel:<br>No dose reduction</li></ul>', 'CDDP<br>Taxol');
INSERT INTO RegimenDetail (pk, SubCancerTypeId2, disp_name, name, schedule, emetogenic_potential, reference, dosage_modifications, brand_names) VALUES (655, 143, 'Capecitabine + Oxaliplatin', '<b>Capecitabine + Oxaliplatin</b>', '<b>Capecitabine</b>1,000 mg/m<sup>2</sup> PO bid on days 1-14<br><b>Oxaliplatin</b>130 mg/m<sup>2</sup> IV on day 1<br>Repeat cycle every 21 days.', 'Moderate', '$Van Meerten E, et al. Br J Cancer 2007;96:1348-1352.$', '<b>Hepatic(Liver)</b><ul><li>Capecitabine:<br>No dose reduction</li></ul><b>Renal(Kidney)</b><ul><li>Capecitabine:<br>If CrCl 30-50 mL/min, reduce dose by 25% <br>                                                                     If CrCl < 30 mL/min, do not use</li></ul>', 'Xeloda<br>Eloxatin, Oxaliplatin, various');
INSERT INTO RegimenDetail (pk, SubCancerTypeId2, disp_name, name, schedule, emetogenic_potential, reference, dosage_modifications, brand_names) VALUES (656, 143, 'ECF', '<b>ECF</b>', '<b>Epirubicin</b>50 mg/m<sup>2</sup> IV on day 1<br><b>Cisplatin</b>60 mg/m<sup>2</sup> IV on day 1<br><b>5-Fluorouracil</b>200 mg/m<sup>2</sup>/day IV continuous infusion for 24 weeks.<br>Repeat cycle every 21 days.', 'High', '$Cunningham D, et al. N Engl J Med 2008;358:36-46.$', '<b>Hepatic(Liver)</b><ul><li>Cisplatin:<br>No dose reduction</li></ul><b>Renal(Kidney)</b><ul><li>Cisplatin:<br>If CrCl 30-60 mL/min, reduce dose by 50%   <br>                                                                   If CrCl < 30 mL/min, do not use</li></ul>', 'CDDP<br>Ellence, various');
